item.title: Xander
item.description: Xander Alexander is a four-year-old from Portland iwth cystic fibrosis. His favorfite colors are red and blue. His favorite show is Mickey Mouse Clubhouse and he likes playing with cars and his pet dog, Captain. Xander is going to Disney World in OCtober and is very excited to meet his favorite character Mickey!
